on there and stuff.

00:26:58.780 --> 00:27:00.640
One in a million chance
can someone like me

00:27:00.640 --> 00:27:02.500
get the opportunity to do that.

00:27:02.500 --> 00:27:04.640
I'm so thankful
that I can do it,

00:27:04.640 --> 00:27:08.612
and it's actually unbelievable
